External Dependencies
=====================

the content of the 'ext/' directory:

  cryptopp -> cryptopp-CRYPTOPP_5_6_5/
  date/
  gitalk/
  pugixml/
  sizebounded/
  boost_1_67_0


gitalk
======

license: BSD3

https://github.com/CodiePP/gitalk.git


sizebounded
===========

license: BSD3

https://github.com/CodiePP/sizebounded.git


date
====

license: MIT

https://github.com/HowardHinnant/date.git


pugixml
=======

parses XML data

license: MIT

https://github.com/zeux/pugixml.git


Crypto++ 7.0.0
==============

license: Boost Software License 1.0

https://github.com/weidai11/cryptopp/releases/tag/CRYPTOPP_7_0_0

the extracted directory should be symlinked to 'cryptopp' so we find 
the headers.

on OSX build with env. var. set:

> export USER_CXXFLAGS="-mmacosx-version-min=10.11"
> ./cryptest.sh fast


Boost 1.67.0
============

license: Boost Software License 1.0

./b2 toolset=clang cflags=-mmacosx-version-min=10.11 cxxflags=-mmacosx-version-min=10.11 mflags=-mmacosx-version-min=10.11 mmflags=-mmacosx-version-min=10.11 linkflags=-mmacosx-version-min=10.11 cxxflags=-std=c++1z stage

